'''罗伯特·韦恩·图利斯'''（{{lang-en|Robert Wayne Tullis}}，{{bd|1950/1951年}}）是美国[[自由意志党|自由意志党]]政治人物。他是[[阿肯色州|阿肯色州]][[矿泉_(阿肯色州)|矿泉城]]市长，曾在1979至1993年间任[[阿肯色州众议院|阿肯色州众议院]]议员。

==传记==
图利斯的父母是丹齐尔·图利斯和妮娜·惠特莫·图利斯<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.arkansasonline.com/obituaries/2011/apr/14/nina-tullis-2011-04-14/|title=Nina Whitmore Tullis|newspaper=Arkansas Democrat-Gazette|date=2011-04-14|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref>。1979年至1993年，他作为[[民主党_(美国)|民主党人]]在[[阿肯色州众议院|阿肯色州众议院]]任职，代表第八十六选区，包括[[霍华德县_(阿肯色州)|霍华德县]]和[[塞维尔县_(阿肯色州)|塞维尔县]]的一部分<ref>{{cite book|title=The Historical Report of the Arkansas Secretary of State 2008|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Gz-uJNyBFOEC&pg=PA236|date=April 2009|publisher=University of Arkansas Press|isbn=978-0-615-23214-0|page=236}}</ref>。1994年，图利斯投入了{{le|阿肯色州审计员|Arkansas State Auditor}}竞选，在民主党初选中以微弱劣势输给了{{le|古斯·温菲尔德|Gus Wingfield}}。2010年，他是[[美国绿党|绿党]]提名的{{le|阿肯色州财政部长|Treasurer of Arkansas}}候选人，输给了现任民主党人{{le|玛莎·肖夫纳|Martha Shoffner}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://independentpoliticalreport.com/2010/07/former-state-rep-running-for-ar-auditor-as-a-green-launches-campaign-with-controversial-ad/#more-17798|title=Former State Rep. running for AR auditor as a Green launches campaign with controversial ad|author=Levin, Ross|publisher=Independent Political Report|date=2010-07-29|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.arktimes.com/ArkansasBlog/archives/2010/07/18/might-shoffner-get-an-opponent|title=Might Shoffner get an opponent?|author=Brantley, Max|newspaper=Arkansas Times|date=2010-07-18|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref>。同年，图利斯竞选[[矿泉_(阿肯色州)|矿泉城]]市长<ref>{{cite web|url=http://media.arkansasonline.com/news/documents/2010/08/25/tullis.pdf|title=Bobby Tullis filings|publisher=Arkansas Secretary of State|date=2010-08-25|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref>。虽然他以46%的得票率获得第一名，但由于他没有获得多数票，必须进行决选，他输掉了决选<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.arktimes.com/ArkansasBlog/archives/2010/11/03/win-some-lose-some/|title=Win some, lose some|author=Brantley, Max|newspaper=Arkansas Times|date=2010-11-03|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref>。

2012年，图利斯竞选[[阿肯色州第四国会选区|阿肯色州第四国会选区]]议员。他最初探索以[[共和党_(美国)|共和党]]和[[自由意志党|自由意志党]]身份参选，后来他支持共和党候选人贝丝·安妮·兰金<ref>{{cite web|url=https://talkbusiness.net/2011/08/elvis-is-back-in-the-building-and-on-the-political-scene/2415/|title=Elvis Is Back In The Building And On The Political Scene|author=Brock, Roby|publisher=Talk Business|date=2011-08-31|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://talkbusiness.net/2011/10/fourth-district-gains-more-candidates-cowart-and-tullis/2732/|title=Fourth District Gains More Candidates – Cowart And Tullis|author=Brock, Roby|publisher=Talk Business|date=2011-10-31|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://talkbusiness.net/2011/12/ross-chief-of-staff-rules-out-fourth-district-run/|title=Ross District Director Rules Out Fourth District Run|author=Brock, Roby|publisher=Talk Business|date=2011-12-12|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref>。图利斯后来决定以自由意志党身份参选，因为兰金未能赢得共和党提名。他输给了共和党人[[汤姆·科顿|汤姆·科顿]]。

2014年，图利斯寻求自由意志党的财政部长提名未果<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.arktimes.com/ArkansasBlog/archives/2014/01/27/am-report-arrest-in-fatal-stabbing-political-announcement|title=AM report: Arrest in fatal stabbing, political announcement|author=Brantley, Max|newspaper=Arkansas Times|date=2014-01-27|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref>。同年，他当选为矿泉城市长<ref>{{cite web|url=https://lpar.org/elections/current-public-office-holders/|title=Current Public Office Holders|publisher=Libertarian Party of Arkansas|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref>。

图利斯是阿肯色州唯一一位担任民选官职的自由意志党人。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.lp.org/elected-officials-2/|title=Elected Officials|publisher=Libertarian Party of the United States|accessdate=2021-01-25}}</ref>

